    <h2>About Feeding America</h2>
    <div class="about">
        <p>Feeding America fights hunger by working with food banks, pantries, and meal programs to provide food to those in need.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="mission">
        <h2>Charity Mission</h2>
        <p>End hunger in the United States by ensuring every individual has access to enough nutritious food. They achieve this by connecting people in need with food resources through a vast network of food banks and partner organizations while also advocating for policies to address the root causes of hunger.</p>
    </div>
